<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.6">
<l>muḻunīlamu malarāmpalu maravintamum viravik</l>
<l>kaḻunīroṭu maṭavāravar kaṇvāymukam malarum</l>
<l>ceḻunīrvayal taḻuvuñciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉam</l>
<l>toḻunīrmaiya tuṭaiyāraṭi toḻuvārtuya rilarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who worship the feet of those with the custom of worshipping</l>
<l>The watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr, embraced by fertile wet fields,</l>
<l>Where maidens’ eyes, lips, and faces appear like large dark lilies,</l>
<l>Blossoming red lilies, lotuses, and dark waterlilies, they will not have sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
